Quote: <i>Scrub fence or shed not to be erected in any town.</i> Throughout, the enactments referring to fences constructed of hazardous material, the term " Scrub " shall be deemed to include manuka scrub, branches, or boughs of the manuka or other shrubs, and all other material of a similarly hazardous description.
